{"word":"G1741 - ἔνδοξος - éndoxos - en'-dox-os - Glorious","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔνδοξος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">éndoxos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en'-dox-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Glorious</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மகிமையானது, அலங்கார, கனவான் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"illustrious, honorable, esteemed, notable, glorious, splendid"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a>; <i>in glory</i>, that is, <i>splendid</i>, (figuratively) <i>noble:</i> - glorious, gorgeous [-ly], honourable.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1380/1380\">G1380</a>, <a href=\"#/G1391/1391\">G1391</a>, <a href=\"#/G1392/1392\">G1392</a>, <a href=\"#/G1740/1740\">G1740</a>, <a href=\"#/G1741/1741\">G1741</a>, <a href=\"#/G3861/3861\">G3861</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>"}]}